README

A Gentoo overlay.

Setting up layman

Edit /etc/layman/layman.cfg:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
overlays  : http://www.gentoo.org/proj/en/overlays/layman-global.txt
            http://www.gitorious.org/viralex-overlay/viralex.git/list.xml

and add the overlay using layman.
			layman -f
			layman -a viralex
